A service to match you with people who have similar conditions so you can exchange information or motivate each other online
Access to a programme where a nurse will check up on you if your measurements are irregular and/or call you if you are not inputting your measurements

Discounted Health Screening benefit every 2 years

A no-claims rebate if no claims are made at the end of your policy tenure. Rebate is 15% of premiums paid.
